<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #CCCCCC" colspan="6">Easy Company experiences the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Bulge" title="Battle of the Bulge">Battle of the Bulge</a> and have to hold ground near <a href="/wiki/Bastogne" title="Bastogne">Bastogne</a>. The episode focuses on <a href="/wiki/Eugene_Roe" title="Eugene Roe">Eugene "Doc" Roe</a> as he helps out his fellow soldiers where he can, while also scrounging for medical supplies, of which the Company is dangerously low.&#160;</td>
